# Variables

@host = http://localhost:80
@prefix = /api/v1
@auth_token = token_here

### Obtener todos los users
GET {{host}}{{prefix}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Obtener un user espec√≠fico   
GET {{host}}{{prefix}}/users/10
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Eliminar un user
DELETE {{host}}{{prefix}}/users/10
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}